{"tid":265644,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【4月新番】Sakura Quest【第 9 話】","createTime":"2017-05-31T19:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T21:40:13.000Z","uid":1402,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1adb9bd7b995cf2b726b3314e7c6f474560ffc79","tid":265644,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T19:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://sakura-quest.com/images/index_mainvisual.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsakura-quest.com%2Fimages%2Findex_mainvisual.jpg&h=c9489a02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSAKURA QUEST<br />\nサクラクエスト<br />\n<br />\n先前由 P.A. 所推出的《花開物語》以及《白箱 SHIROBAKO》，都是以描述職場生活以及角色成長為主題的動畫作品。而他們預定將於明年春季推出的《SAKURA QUEST》，則是將以「區域振興」為主。 <br />\n<br />\n求職不順遂的女主角「木春由乃」，意外的被任命為「間野山」這個鄉下地方的「國王」，她將為了振興地方觀光，與其他 4 位女孩子們，在一年內為地方觀光共同努力，並且讓自身成長的故事。<br />\n<br />\nPV<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3WRZKPidbf8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3WRZKPidbf8&d=Ii6SpWfcqDH85TvitJNNTJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=1472c9a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3WRZKPidbf8</a><br />\n<br />\n──STAFF──<br />\n原作：Alexandre S. D. Celibidache<br />\n監督：増井壮一<br />\n系列構成：横谷昌宏<br />\n腳本：横谷昌宏、入江信吾<br />\n角色原案：BUNBUN<br />\n角色設計、總作畫監督：関口可奈味<br />\n美術監督：佐藤歩<br />\n色彩設計：中野尚美<br />\n撮影監督：横山翼<br />\n3D監督：小川耕平<br />\n編集：高橋歩<br />\n音響監督：飯田里樹<br />\n動畫製作：P.A.WORKS<br />\n<br />\n──CAST──<br />\n木春 由乃：七瀬彩夏<br />\n四ノ宮 しおり：上田麗奈<br />\n緑川 真希：安済知佳<br />\n織部 凛々子：田中ちえ美<br />\n香月 早苗：小松未可子<br />\n門田 丑松：斧アツシ<br />\n美濃：濱野大輝<br />\n山田：下野紘<br />\n高見澤：小西克幸<br />\n桑達魯：ヴィナイ・マーシー<br />\n安潔莉卡：森なな子<br />\n鈴木 エリカ：黒沢ともよ<br />\n織部 千登勢：.伊沢磨紀<br />\n<br />\n──放送──<br />\nTOKYO MX 水曜日 24：00～<br />\nAT-X 水曜日24：00<br />\nニコニコ生放送 金曜日23:00<br />\n<br />\n──【廣告】繁體字幕 <a href=\"http://ebb.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Febb.io&d=Ii6SpWfcqDH85TvitJNNTJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=dc3897b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ebb.io</a>──<br />\n是咪想快啲睇到繁體字幕新番？<br />\n即刻將 <a href=\"http://ebb.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Febb.io&d=Ii6SpWfcqDH85TvitJNNTJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=dc3897b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://ebb.io</a> 加入書籤啦!"},{"pid":"cfc2fdb266ee85aecd8169dd23a2b6ced1ad9d47","tid":265644,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T19:43:28.000Z","msg":"又開錯台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86095164b35d4eaa02c16dc41d7743fbf5d75a3","tid":265644,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T20:00:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又開錯台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d471a1195a30fd8122c6afd87fdc2ce6ba4a30ea","tid":265644,"uid":119408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T01:04:45.000Z","msg":"部素麵機射到國王一身都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1e704f2b0e835accb94dc0164e516cf5de26c6","tid":265644,"uid":50131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T01:08:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>部素麵機射到國王一身都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n究竟係空中飛出黎要點接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw由乃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6725e435101c66aae7a3aeb63fece247c24bc5d7","tid":265644,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T01:34:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>部素麵機射到國王一身都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n究竟係空中飛出黎要點接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw由乃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/asset